commitResults.messageBody:
- Added full predicate support for Subject, Level, Price, and Role filters.
- Implemented flexible FindCommandParser to handle multiple values per prefix
  (e.g. /s Math /s English) and multi-word inputs (e.g. /s Math Science).
- Enabled AND-combined predicates across all fields for refined search results.
- Added robust exception handling for invalid inputs and malformed ranges.
- Updated FindCommand usage message to clarify prefix order flexibility and
  support for multiple values per prefix.
- Improved overall code readability, documentation, and Javadoc consistency.
